Employer State Compliance Roadmap

The Employer State Compliance Roadmap allows you to review and understand key human resources and payroll compliance requirements through an easily accessible state-by-state database. Available through an annual subscription, the Roadmap is updated quarterly to keep you informed of the latest laws and legislative changes.

Below are the available subscription options to fit your company's needs:

State bundle 1 state 2-5 states 6-15 states 16+ states
Price/year $800 $1,500 $3,500 $5,000

Each subscription bundle comes with two user licenses. Additional licenses can be purchased for $500/user license.
